We are seeking a highly skilled Data Engineer with expertise in managing, designing, and optimizing data pipelines utilizing Apache Airflow, Snowflake, and Apache Kafka. You will play a pivotal role in architecting robust, scalable, and efficient data solutions, ensuring the integrity, reliability, and accessibility of our data infrastructure




